genresAdvancedInfo.name: lapland hip hop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Lapland hip hop is a unique blend of traditional Sami music and modern hip hop beats. The lyrics often touch on themes of identity, cultural pride, and political issues. The music incorporates traditional Sami instruments such as the joik and the luohti, giving it a distinct sound.
